### BANTI SCHOOL MANAGEMENT SYSTEM

# BANTI SCHOOL ADMINISTRATION
The administration section will deal with day to day running of the school.

Attendance logging for staff and students

Class performance monitoring

Staff performance monitoring

Student performance monitoring

Result uploading

Payments [school fees, Salary]

# BANTI SCHOOL ACADEMICS
    This subsection will handle all academic related activities which includes
    <ul>
        <li>Creation of courses and course modules</li>
        <li> Class scheduling </li>

        <li> Course registration </li>    
    </ul>